2:T719,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is D-ID better than Opus Clip?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. D-ID scores 7.0 overall while Opus Clip scores 8.0. D-ID is best for developers needing talking head API and quick avatar videos, while Opus Clip excels for YouTubers repurposing to Shorts/Reels and podcast clipping."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, D-ID or Opus Clip?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"D-ID starts at $5.99/mo and Opus Clip starts at $15/mo. D-ID offers a free plan. Opus Clip offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from D-ID to Opus Clip?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both D-ID and Opus Clip support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about D-ID vs Opus Clip?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, D-ID holds an overall rating of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10. Opus Clip has an overall rating of 8/10 and ease of use score of 9/10. Users praise D-ID for affordable entry price and Opus Clip for excellent ai clip selection."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, D-ID or Opus Clip?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Opus Clip for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, D-ID remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize affordable entry price. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"oWPZTPCPUwZMl312gxRMA","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","div",n